						<summary>

						<p>Sides of the <hi rend="italic">balipītha</hi> in front of the Paḍu temple.</p>						

						<p>1118 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This incomplete and damaged record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1041, Viḷaṁbi Makara-saṅkramaṇa, Utare-nakshatra, Wednesday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1118, A.D., December 25, f.d.n., ·66.</hi> The <hi rend="italic">pūrnimā</hi> referred to in the record occurred on Sunday the 29th.</p>						

						<p>It refers to the rule of some king and mentions Basava.</p>						

